  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Once Upon A Mind - A Little Too Friendly</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A short, story-driven psychological horror experience. With voice acting.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emily, 23, moves to Brooklyn in search of a fresh start her own space, her own life. The apartment is cozy, the landlady is kind, and the small café around the corner offers her a quick job. Everything feels like it’s falling into place… until it isn’t.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLEASE USE HEADPHONES FOR BETTER EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Voice Acting</strong> – Most lines of dialogue and monologue is now voiced, bringing the story's tension and emotions to life when needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Graphic Novel </strong>– Dive into key story sequences presented in a fully voiced, stylized graphic novel format for deeper emotional impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/92b866175b7d24be18e2ce5a461f8b93.avif?t=1755429449\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras_big/92b866175b7d24be18e2ce5a461f8b93.avif?t=1755429449 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Grounded psychological horror</strong> – No ghosts. No monsters. Just people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Narrative-driven</strong> – Experience a chilling story told through dialogue, monologue, and immersive atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/6f40a2dafc45a3db7a0e667942f5a449.poster.avif?t=1755429449\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/6f40a2dafc45a3db7a0e667942f5a449.webm?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/6f40a2dafc45a3db7a0e667942f5a449.mp4?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Short & focused</strong> – Designed to be completed in under an hour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Realistic tone</strong> – Inspired by real-life situations of obsession, control, and unease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>First-person exploration</strong> – Interact with your surroundings and uncover the story at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/cd1437d9cbc21ca6299124accebedb0c.poster.avif?t=1755429449\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/cd1437d9cbc21ca6299124accebedb0c.webm?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/cd1437d9cbc21ca6299124accebedb0c.mp4?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Cozy Style Graphics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/25e0692269d671aa33f43dbae7a3abcf.avif?t=1755429449\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras_big/25e0692269d671aa33f43dbae7a3abcf.avif?t=1755429449 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔹Calm café gameplay – Experience gentle, peaceful moments during café shifts.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/72d73aa49eac7c3819a40dc61fd538a6.poster.avif?t=1755429449\" width=352 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/72d73aa49eac7c3819a40dc61fd538a6.webm?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3690750/extras/72d73aa49eac7c3819a40dc61fd538a6.mp4?t=1755429449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAME TIME: 40-60 Minutes.</strong></p>",
